# Integration gate (foreman-v2)

Before **every commit** in this repository, run:

`./scripts/integration-check.sh`

from the foreman-v2 root (`/Users/jonathanborgia/foreman-git/foreman-v2`). Fix any **FAIL** results that are in scope for your change before pushing.

## Re-run when touching integration surfaces

Run `./scripts/integration-check.sh` again after edits to any of:

- `scripts/paperclip-openclaw-executor.sh`
- `scripts/provision.sh`
- `scripts/configure.sh`
- `config/openclaw.foreman.json`

Treat a non-zero exit from the script as a blocker for commit when failures are caused by or related to your changes.
